OL,3,CJersey tourism numbers struggle to
OL,4,Creach pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,F's tourism industry is struggling to
OL,7,Fbounce back to pre-Covid levels, new
OL,8,Fvisitor figures reveal.
OL,10,Fhas released statistics for 2023
OL,11,Fvisitor numbers as it works on a new
OL,12,Fcampaign to encourage more tourists to
OL,13,Fthe island.
OL,15,FThe latest data shows around 527,000
OL,16,Fpeople visited Jersey in 2023 - an 11%
OL,17,Fincrease from the year before.
OL,19,FBut this was 31% down from 2019, which
OL,20,Fsaw 770,700 total visitors according
OL,21,Fto the website.
