OL,3,CJersey tourism numbers struggle to
OL,4,Creach pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,FThere are signs of recovery, however,
OL,7,Fas overnight visits in 2023 increase
OL,8,Fby 8% from the year before, with the
OL,9,Faverage length of stay also increasing
OL,10,Ffrom 2022.
OL,12,FTo drive more tourists to the island,
OL,13,FVisit Jersey will launch a new
OL,14,Fcampaign for the spring and summer,
OL,15,Falong with a brand new video advert.
OL,17,F'Where Sea Meets Soul' will target
OL,18,Fyounger audiences and will launch
OL,19,Facross France and Germany, as well as
OL,20,Fthe UK, to reach European tourists.
