OL,3,CJersey tourism numbers struggle to
OL,4,Creach pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,FVisit Jersey states: "The new campaign
OL,7,Fis driven by the goal of increasing
OL,8,Fovernight leisure visits, which have
OL,9,Fbeen the slowest category to recover
OL,10,Fpost-Covid."
OL,12,FVisit Jersey CEO Tricia Warwick hopes
OL,13,Fthe new advert rebrands Jersey as a
OL,14,Fscenic destination that draws in
OL,15,Frepeat visitors, paralleling places
OL,16,Flike Wales and Scotland's panoramic
OL,17,Flandscapes, rather than competing with
OL,18,FMediterranean destinations.
