OL,3,CJersey tourism numbers struggle to
OL,4,Creach pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,FShe said: "The bucket and spade appeal
OL,7,Fwas a long time ago, but life's moved
OL,8,Fon and I think we need to be more
OL,9,Fauthentic about what Jersey is and
OL,10,Fwhat it can offer visitors as well.
OL,12,F"For the first time, we're going into
OL,13,Fcinema. The aerial imagery we're using
OL,14,Fof Jersey really portrays the island
OL,15,Ffrom a different aspect and surprises
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,18,F"And that's what you need - you need
OL,19,Fto surprise, you need to get cut
OL,20,Fthrough, and you need to get people to
OL,21,Fconsider Jersey."
